{"tid":638144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羽生結弦凱旋遊行 12萬粉絲熱情上街","createTime":"2018-04-22T12:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T11:11:26.000Z","uid":31255,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"062386cb90430c0571be32a2a3e9882ba26d6996","tid":638144,"uid":31255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:42:40.000Z","msg":"日本男子花滑選手羽生結弦，今年2月在南韓平昌冬奧，蟬聯男子花滑項目金牌，而他的故鄉宮城縣仙台市，今天也為他舉辦了盛大的凱旋遊行活動，吸引近12萬國內外粉絲熱情參與。<br />\n<br />\n22號一大早，宮城縣仙台市的主要道路兩旁，即使氣溫高達29度，但依舊擋不住熱情粉絲，高舉海報或維尼熊娃娃，來參加花滑選手羽生結弦的平昌冬奧凱旋遊行<br />\n<br />\n羽生結弦在2月的平昌冬奧男子花滑項目中，雖然帶傷，但再次勇奪金牌，在老家仙台市舉行的凱旋遊行，吸引國內外粉絲徹夜排隊卡位，爭睹花滑王子風采。<br />\n<br />\n早在4年前羽生首次奪金時，當時的凱旋遊行就吸引了9萬多人共襄盛舉，這次主辦單位推估，這次遊行的參加人數，還將更進一步達到12萬人的新高。<br />\n<br />\n戴上冬奧金牌，23歲的羽生笑容靦腆，對台下的民眾不停揮手，並接過宮城縣知事頒發的榮譽市民獎狀。<br />\n<br />\n日本男子花滑選手羽生結弦表示，「這次可以二連霸，帶著金牌回到仙台來真的很開心，我胸口的這面金牌，真的是多虧了大家的支持和加油，我將會把這份喜悅和光景，以及大家的加油聲謹記在心，繼續努力下去。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/a3bde5e7-5636-48a2-a78c-e34e69c1269f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2Fa3bde5e7-5636-48a2-a78c-e34e69c1269f.jpg&h=7242093d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緊接著羽生便搭上特製車輛，展開長約1公里，歷時40分鐘的凱旋遊行。只見車頂上的羽生，不停向道路兩旁的爆量人潮賣力揮手，接受民眾歡呼。而民眾在欣喜之餘，也期待這位日本花滑王子，未來還能帶給世人更多驚奇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DbYfznWU8AAbWoj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDbYfznWU8AAbWoj.jpg&h=a98b05bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DbYf3XOUwAAOETu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDbYf3XOUwAAOETu.jpg&h=90767de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DbYb6IdV4AIVn-O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDbYb6IdV4AIVn-O.jpg&h=4055e5e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DbXTrYnU8AApQoW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDbXTrYnU8AApQoW.jpg&h=4a800c08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c68a457a384da80f6115b6cd041f965730694139","tid":638144,"uid":31255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hlG2TwPjJlA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhlG2TwPjJlA&d=nBFEAOULz8l72pXpn6iQDZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a6e75825\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hlG2TwPjJlA</a>"},{"pid":"9a74a130e5f8102f076b0de9721d1315f30dd3dd","tid":638144,"uid":7840,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:48:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f63bba346613f7977ca02be2f5d683066dd839c5","tid":638144,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"人生贏家，好過好多濕鳩藝人"},{"pid":"0361a496fd588d79a25ff358d6967dec27038ec6","tid":638144,"uid":73232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:54:15.000Z","msg":"希望佢退役唔好入娛樂圈<br />\n唔可以無咗呢股清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a39c259bfb26550095f1c0fe0348e15724fe951","tid":638144,"uid":26519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"好正<br />\n好似動漫入面d王子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a994aef0601f4e284c125110238d946e49b6f5d4","tid":638144,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"真係好屈機"},{"pid":"278e1263236432d70d0cccc74a88b4784cdd6ff4","tid":638144,"uid":73232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"技術 表演力 都得<br />\n真係全能型 <br />\n份人性格又堅強 成日爆seed <br />\n人品又好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4bd07926912b6b3431abe268c8eae45d77c8c4","tid":638144,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-2